      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="f95c3561-eef7-493d-a776-0be400598603" type="Adjective">
          <Vi>đúng, chính xác</Vi>
          <En>Free from error; in accordance with fact or truth.</En>
          <Example>The answer is correct; you solved the problem perfectly.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="fed3dfcd-e2f5-4b62-9da1-107ecd0f1f76">
              <Vi>Khi kiểm tra bài làm, giáo viên xác nhận học sinh trả lời đúng.</Vi>
              <En>When grading a test, the teacher confirms the student's answer is accurate.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="68e8d65b-ee74-437a-8cb6-107c8c8de30e">
              <Vi>Trong lập trình, một đoạn mã đúng về mặt logic và cú pháp.</Vi>
              <En>In programming, a code segment that is logically and syntactically correct.</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
